Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的名字是古屋螢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天開始上高中一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我有个引以為豪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:17.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一個作為班委團結著班級的很厲害的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:20.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然因為太過認真找不到女朋友很可憐就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:25.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,古屋君 又在同一個班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川同學 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:29.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:34.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我哥哥承蒙你關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這麼客氣 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 只是客套話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥 這個人誰 只是同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,關係好嗎 還有其他女性朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 螢 很沒禮貌耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:50.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你很喜歡你哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈? 你在說啥? 這很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 這傢伙是兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是挺好的嗎 挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以你是我哥的什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,莫非難道說 你們兩個在交往中?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 我們只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:13.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我早就覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:14.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,暫時唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:23.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是沒有得到回應 所以說是暫時啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:26.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這傢伙在耍著你玩 怎麼回應早就想好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 快點拒絕她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,讓她懷有希望很可憐的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:36.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢… 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是啊古屋君 要拒絕的話就快點吖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:46.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 我 並 並不是對皆川同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:50.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拒絕她 拒絕她 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也 也不是不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我在擔心你啊為什麼就不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你在被玩弄 就算交往也只會受傷而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢 並不是說要交往唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我這是被拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,女朋友什麼的不需要吧 因為有我就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 皆川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我沒辦法輕鬆說出交往吧這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為交往之後那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,結婚什麼的 沒有經濟能力的話孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我們的事情你已經考慮到這種地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然不是這樣的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是因為我哥人比較認真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是啊 真的很認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以才喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:38.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我再試著等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小螢 能先幫我看著麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可以 我不會把哥哥讓給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒關係的唷 我會一起疼愛你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是討厭!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我沒什麼特別喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:59.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能熱衷的興趣和愛好也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我自己都覺得自己是無聊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是大家真的有那麼多喜歡的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看起來喜歡星星呢 要不要加入天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 並沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 嘛 只是聊聊天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,決定了要加什麼社團了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:23.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那要不要來看看星之管弦樂呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 玩笑過頭啦!? 啊勒勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看星星很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那是當然啊 這麼好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是只是看的話不會厭倦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:41.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,會厭倦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有別的特點什麼的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有! 簡單地說就是天文部很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在脫單率高達100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 是不是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩你並不是那麼喜歡星星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那為什麼要在天文部?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 你看 我喜歡天文部的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 還有些什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜託了! 反正你沒有其他想加的社團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:16.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我說一個讓你對星星感興趣的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那塊區域有一個叫做角宿一的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看起來是一個非常大的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但其實是兩顆相互環繞吸引的星星喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,兩顆星星共同努力的話就可以發出如此耀眼的光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是不是有點哲學味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:35.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:36.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有興趣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(1400,200)\fn方正喵呜_GBK\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明完全照抄學長的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有其他的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(1000,0)\fn方正喵呜_GBK\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明感覺受教了很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看火星時吃的章魚燒 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:55.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已經畢業了的前輩說什麼火星人應該就像章魚一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以就一邊看火星一邊烤章魚燒
Comment: 0,0:05:56.38,0:06:01.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn方正喵呜_GBK\bord1.2\c&H00050606}然後一邊看火星一邊烤章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是前輩一直在看火星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我一個人大口大口地吃完了
Comment: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:08.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是前輩一直在看火星 所以我一個人大口大口地吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:08.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}然後前輩就超級生氣 本來他平時臉就好可怕了啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}其他的比如還有秋天賞月呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:14.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏天一邊熱火超天地講著外星人的恐怖故事一遍吃冰棒什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:15.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已經跟星星沒有關係了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對這個人而言 天文部是真的非常喜歡的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也能像這樣熱衷於什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加賀也來嘛 肯定很會有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我沒有什麼特別喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一邊覺得這樣的自己很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一邊尋找著自己喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這就是我在尋找的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:44.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總而言之我 想要多看看這份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:49.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:55.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,鄰座的上根同學 總是迴避著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根還不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,馬 馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不願和我對上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我做了什麼不好的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還是趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛 剛田君!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:24.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的隱形眼鏡掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:29.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我出去的時候會注意不踩到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想要你陪我一起找啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明白了 一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我沒被討厭嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你經常掉隱形眼鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如想要擦擦汗的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這汗確實不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:49.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實你有話想對我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我已經做好準備 盡全力回應上根的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想說什麼就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,既然你都說到這種份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,應該已經知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在暫時 還沒什麼頭緒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前上課的時候呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我因為眼睛不好正在苦惱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你把筆記借給我過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那件事怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為 好溫柔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是多管閒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有注意到真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才沒有! 不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找隱形眼鏡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,至少請讓我幫你找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:48.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答覆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:51.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答覆?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 也沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的感情 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也只是想傳達給你而已… 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這意思是 想看到我的誠意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不至於
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是 想知道剛田的想法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:07.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果這樣能得到你的原諒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我其實 一直都理解不了女生的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 沒那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果再接近你的話 肯定會給你添更多麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這麼沒用的我 以後還是承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:39.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哼～ 隱形眼鏡找到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎麼哭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才你是 能和我交往的意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交往?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顧的話 肯定是要交往的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝謝——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 上根??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我說的話很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:03.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 我這邊才是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我還沒 好好的告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註釋：告白在日語本意是說出實話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了? 有什麼話想說就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,未報的雨 落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 沒帶傘嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,同班的菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,幾乎沒和他說過什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,借給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 跑回去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:42.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為感覺很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,中途還是一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 和女生一起回家的話會很難堪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也沒有 和高野一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:02.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 和我這種人傳不出什麼緋聞的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,肩膀淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那再靠近點?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 再近點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 不會不好意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和男生 這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 也沒人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 要是被喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到了之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 我也沒這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎麼笑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,戀愛這種事情我不是太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你要是被表白了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:40.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種人不存在的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是假設啦 假設你被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概會拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為 對我這種人表白 他肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我又不可愛 又陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有這種事!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野你幫別人做衛生什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,每天照顧班裡的青鱂魚之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我 對高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我要在這裡坐公車了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才 你對我說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣 那拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}戀愛嗎… 對我來說太勉強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}菅原君這麼溫柔 肯定很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊勒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}剛才 要對你說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然還是決定要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我 我對高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喜 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你是在 鼓勵我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:58.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:03.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那 我在這裡下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}咦? Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}菅原君這個人 真是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}作為借傘的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}給他做點餅乾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 至近距離戀愛
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也會覺得很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}此時此刻也在想念著你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}喜歡與討厭相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的機率的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還是跨不出這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們的關係可以說是曖昧模糊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雖然無聊但還是希望能感受到屬於我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要珍視這份感情
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.90,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:36.07,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:40.57,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.41,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.87,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:52.25,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:57.67,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:04.22,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:09.39,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:15.27,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:21.36,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ただそれだけでいいのに
